T02TD3162E:181a-1: ha ri ha ri ha ri b'a ha na s'a dha nam /
T02TD3162E:181a-3: seng ge dang bya khyung dang khyab 'jug la bzhugs pa'i sgrub thabs /
T02TD3162E:181a-4: sngar brjod pa'i rim pa nyid kyis stong pa nyid bsgoms pa'i rjes thogs la /
T02TD3162E:181a-5: yi ge hr'i: dkar po yongs su rdzogs par gyur pa las /
T02TD3162E:181a-6: seng ge dang bya khyung dang khyab 'jug la bzhugs pa las byung ba'i bcom ldan 'das spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug tu bdag nyid bsgom par bya ste /
T02TD3162E:181a-7: sku thams cad dkar ba ral ba dang dbu rgyan dang ldan pa zhi ba'i cha byad can phyag g-yas pas bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs pa dbang du mdzad pa /
T02TD3162E:181a-8: gnyis pas phreng ba bsnams pa gsum pas tshul ngan par gnas pa'i 'jig rten pa rnams ston par mdzad do //
T02TD3162E:181a-9: g-yon pas dbyug tho bsnams pa gnyis pas ri dags krishna sa ri'i phags pa bsnams pa /
T02TD3162E:181a-10: gsum pas ril pa spyi blugs bsnams pa'o //
T02TD3162E:181a-11: seng ge dang bya khyung dang khyab 'jug gi phrag pa na gnas par ro //
T02TD3162E:181a-12: aom hr'i: h'um zhes pa'i sngags 'di bzlas par bya ba'o //
T02TD3162E:181a-13: seng ge dang bya khyung dang khyab 'jug la bzhugs pa las 'byung ba'i sgrub thabs so //
T02TD3162E:181a-14: dge slong tshul khrims rgyal mtshan gyis bsgyur ba'o//
